_sText:
A map with two identical sides divided by a central wall. 

~Features~
-multiple levels of walkways around and above the wall
-ladders to reach upper levels
-bunkers on upper level
-lots of cover
-20 spawns per team

Note: Will NOT work with bots. They will just run repeatedly into the wall.
Other Note: HDR was not added due to weird coloring of hands.
